<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.9.10">
<l>pārmaṉṉu tolpukaḻp pallavar kōṉpaṇin tapara mēccura viṇṇakarmēl</l>
<l>kārmaṉṉu nīḷvayal maṅkaiyar tantalai vaṉkali kaṉṟikuṉ ṟāturaitta</l>
<l>cīrmaṉṉu centamiḻ mālaival lārttiru māmakaḷ taṉṉaru ḷālulakil</l>
<l>tērmaṉṉa rāyoli mākaṭal cūḻceḻu nīrula kāṇṭuti kaḻvarkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master this garland of fine Tamil, in which excellence endures,</l>
<l rend="indent">composed without error</l>
<l>By Kalikaṉṟi, chief of those of Maṅkai with vast fields where rain endures,</l>
<l rend="indent">on Paramēccura Viṇṇakaram</l>
<l>Where bowed the king of the Pallavas of ancient fame</l>
<l rend="indent">which endures [in this] world, they, by the grace of the great lady Tiru,</l>
<l>Will be renowned on earth as chariot[-driving] kings,</l>
<l rend="indent">ruling the earth with fertile waters encircled by the great, roaring seas.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
